# Mikro-ORM auto-generated schema snapshots — regenerated locally on every
# db:generate / db:migrate. Tracking them in git caused a major incident
# 2026-04-29 (snapshot got out of sync, db:generate produced a migration
# that DROPped every Medusa core table; db:migrate executed it and wiped
# the production DB). Treat as build artifacts.
src/modules/**/migrations/.snapshot-*.json

